## CMD-11: Interviewer 403 Permission Check — All Routes

```
$ for route in summary stages by-job by-channel stage-duration action-impact insights drilldown refresh-snapshot; do
  method="GET"
  [ "$route" = "refresh-snapshot" ] && method="POST"
  status=$(curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}" -X $method \
    "http://localhost:3000/api/analytics/recruitment-funnel/$route?dateFrom=2025-01-01&dateTo=2026-06-28" \
    -H "Cookie: session=interviewer-session-token")
  echo "  /$route → HTTP $status"
done

  /summary → HTTP 403
  /stages → HTTP 403
  /by-job → HTTP 403
  /by-channel → HTTP 403
  /stage-duration → HTTP 403
  /action-impact → HTTP 403
  /insights → HTTP 403
  /drilldown → HTTP 403
  /refresh-snapshot → HTTP 403
```

**结果**: 9/9 routes 对 interviewer 返回 403。  
